reviewText: Two seperate movies/stories. 1st one is 30 minutes long, no nudity. 2nd one is about an hour long. two scenes of nudity of the same woman. 1st one is of her topless taking a shower. 2nd one is of her topless after her shirt is ripped off. If you blink you'll miss it. You kind of get a full frontal of her but your looking through a windshield which makes it a little blurry and she is running.
Don't waste your money. No sex, no nudity. Not even midrift which is shown on the cover. Film does not deliver.
I was tormented watching this flick, it looks like it was made in someones back yard.
